Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.59,0:00:04.02,Default2,,0,0,0,,Reporting in.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.02,0:00:08.15,Default2,,0,0,0,,Yesterday, an election match was held involving Yuriko Nishinotoin.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.14,0:00:16.62,Default2,,0,0,0,,How can this be...? I was playing... perfectly...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.43,0:00:24.19,Default2,,0,0,0,,Miss Yuriko! Miss Yuriko! Won't someone... please...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.19,0:00:27.81,Default2,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear. Giving up so soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.81,0:00:30.13,Default2,,0,0,0,,How pathetically fragile.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.83,0:00:35.89,Default2,,0,0,0,,Nishinotoin was defeated, and all her chips were given to Inbami and Yobami.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.64,0:00:38.29,Default2,,0,0,0,,It stinks!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.29,0:00:41.15,Default2,,0,0,0,,This whole thing stinks.
