Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.28,0:01:03.65,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)}As you wish, I will gamble with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.28,0:01:03.65,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)}nozomidoori ni kakete ageru {\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.65,0:01:06.50,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)}I won't go easy on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.65,0:01:06.50,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)}tekagen wa shinai {\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.50,0:01:10.04,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)}Love, hate, love, hate.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.50,0:01:10.04,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)}suki kirai suki kirai {\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.04,0:01:13.55,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)}Who will be first?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.04,0:01:13.55,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)}saisho wa dare? {\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.55,0:01:16.97,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)}Moderation is boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.55,0:01:16.97,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)}hodohodo ja tsumannai {\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.97,0:01:19.90,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)}It's all or nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.97,0:01:19.90,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)}subete ka zero ka {\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.90,0:01:23.56,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)}Love, hate, love, hate.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.90,0:01:23.56,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)}suki kirai suki kirai {\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.56,0:01:26.97,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)}Let's have some fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.56,0:01:26.97,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)}tanoshimimashou {\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.63,0:01:38.66,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)}It feels good when you indulge.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.63,0:01:38.66,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)}nomerikomu hou ga kimochi ii {\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.61,0:01:46.81,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)}I'll live, live, live, live a story of wonderful thrills.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.61,0:01:46.81,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)}suteki na suriru no sutoorii wo ikiru ikiru ikiru ikiru {\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.96,0:01:53.55,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)}We won't lose anything of importance.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.96,0:01:53.55,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)}ushinau mono wa takaga shireteru {\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.55,0:02:00.27,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)}We may lose our tomorrow, but not our whole future.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.55,0:02:00.27,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)}ashita wo nakushitemo mirai ga nakunarutte wake janai {\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.27,0:02:06.78,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)}If you want to dream, you need to be world-weary.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.27,0:02:06.78,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)}yume wo miru ni wa shirisugita jidai sa{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.78,0:02:11.31,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)}Come here, and gather round.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.78,0:02:11.31,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)}oide yo kono yubi tomare{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.31,0:02:14.96,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)}I prefer to love until there's nothing left.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.31,0:02:14.96,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)}aishikiru sore ga watashi no tashinami{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.14,0:02:31.06,Default2,,0,0,0,,Here we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.06,0:02:33.83,Default2,,0,0,0,,Thank you for taking me, Suzui.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.83,0:02:35.40,Default2,,0,0,0,,Why did you need to be here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.26,0:02:39.05,Default2,,0,0,0,,Look! It's an invitation to gamble.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.07,0:02:44.81,ElectionMatchNote,,0,0,0,,{\be1{\frx2\fry358\org(620,520)\frz353.9\move(608,588,651.2,480.8,6,423)} after school today in Lounge 7.{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.07,0:02:44.81,ElectionMatchNote,,0,0,0,,{\be1\move(628,396,684,285.6,6,423)}{\frx2\fry358\frz354\org(710,318)\pos(628,396)}An election match will be held
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.07,0:02:44.81,ElectionMatchNote,,0,0,0,,{\be1\move(646,250,714.8,149.2,6,423)}{\frx2\fry358\pos(646,250)\frz354\org(768,114)}{Letter}To the Esteemed Yumeko Jabami
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.36,0:02:40.25,Default2,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.25,0:02:44.81,Default2,,0,0,0,,I'm very thankful to Kirari for the chance to gamble so often.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.81,0:02:47.30,Default2,,0,0,0,,Who gave you this letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.36,0:02:50.31,Default2,,0,0,0,,Oh, I just can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.14,0:02:52.02,Default2,,0,0,0,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.44,0:02:57.44,Default2,,0,0,0,,You're Rei Batsubami, from yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.44,0:02:59.07,Default2,,0,0,0,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.07,0:03:02.54,Default2,,0,0,0,,I am simply showing these ladies the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.53,0:03:07.41,Default2,,0,0,0,,This is Miss Miri Yobami and Miss Miyo Inbami.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.41,0:03:12.03,Default2,,0,0,0,,Our blood relation may be distant, but this is the first time we've met, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.03,0:03:13.33,Default2,,0,0,0,,Yumeko Jabami.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.33,0:03:15.84,Default2,,0,0,0,,That's right. It's nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.84,0:03:18.34,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So they  {\i0}are{\i1} Yumeko's relatives.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.34,0:03:20.92,Default2,,0,0,0,,As you are here as well, that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.92,0:03:23.64,Default2,,0,0,0,,You received this letter too, Yumeko.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.64,0:03:27.22,Default2,,0,0,0,,Oh, my! We can all gamble together, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.22,0:03:29.83,Default2,,0,0,0,,Please don't go too hard on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.83,0:03:32.02,Default2,,0,0,0,,Miyo, no need to act humble.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.08,0:03:35.27,Default2,,0,0,0,,This woman is our enemy, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.11,0:03:38.57,Default2,,0,0,0,,Come now, that won't do, Miri.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.57,0:03:41.90,Default2,,0,0,0,,We're all members of the Momobami Clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.90,0:03:46.28,Default2,,0,0,0,,Let's swear on our family's pride to have a fair and proper match.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.28,0:03:49.16,Default2,,0,0,0,,Yes, let's! I'm looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.17,0:03:57.67,Default2,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy to meet you, Yumeko.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.11,0:04:01.17,Default2,,0,0,0,,I am too, Miyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.41,0:04:05.94,Default2,,0,0,0,,Your turn, Miri!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.92,0:04:11.09,Default2,,0,0,0,,I will now take my leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.56,0:04:17.44,Default2,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're finally here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.30,0:04:20.07,Default2,,0,0,0,,Runa Yomotsuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.69,0:04:23.45,Default2,,0,0,0,,Why is the head of the Election Management Committee here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.52,0:04:28.20,Default2,,0,0,0,,I'm just here to supervise, like any Committee member would.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.78,0:04:31.04,Default2,,0,0,0,,Though, having said that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.58,0:04:40.61,Default2,,0,0,0,,Honestly, I kinda wanted to meet the pair who brought down Yuriko.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.43,0:04:42.34,Default2,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.34,0:04:46.47,Default2,,0,0,0,,Under the supervision of a {\i1}neutral{\i0}  Election Management Committee member,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.47,0:04:51.47,Default2,,0,0,0,,Yuriko lost the gamble {\i1}fair and square{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.93,0:04:53.22,Default2,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.37,0:04:55.31,Default2,,0,0,0,,Yes... of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.31,0:05:00.69,Default2,,0,0,0,,So if you two are gonna play Yumeko Jabami and I'm the dealer,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.69,0:05:03.74,Default2,,0,0,0,,I've got to watch you {\i1}very carefully{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.76,0:05:08.12,Default2,,0,0,0,,I would like nothing more than for you to do your duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.12,0:05:12.12,Default2,,0,0,0,,It's quite reassuring to have the chairwoman as our dealer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.73,0:05:17.29,Default2,,0,0,0,,All right! Let's get started, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.29,0:05:22.17,Default2,,0,0,0,,So... The contestants are Miyo Inbami, Miri Yobami,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.17,0:05:24.24,Default2,,0,0,0,, and Yumeko Jabami. Any objections?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.24,0:05:25.13,Default2,,0,0,0,,I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.86,0:05:28.01,Default2,,0,0,0,,I'll enter this election match too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.61,0:05:32.27,Default2,,0,0,0,,If those two are okay with it, then that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.87,0:05:34.52,Default2,,0,0,0,,I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.11,0:05:37.85,Default2,,0,0,0,,Suzui!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.27,0:05:40.94,Default2,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.94,0:05:43.03,Default2,,0,0,0,,Let's savor every moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.03,0:05:45.28,Default2,,0,0,0,,R... right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.17,0:05:48.33,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's something fishy about this.\N{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.89,0:05:53.28,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I hope I can help Yumeko just a little by entering.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.29,0:05:59.51,Default2,,0,0,0,,All right. To keep things fair, how about we play the game I brought with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.51,0:06:00.67,Default2,,0,0,0,,Fine by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.67,0:06:04.34,Default2,,0,0,0,,Okay! The game you four will be playing is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.34,0:06:06.42,Default2,,0,0,0,,Nim Zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.42,0:06:09.09,Default2,,0,0,0,,There are four types of cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.09,0:06:13.06,Default2,,0,0,0,,The deck has ten cards each of zeros, ones, twos, and threes, for a total of 40 cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.06,0:06:16.20,Default2,,0,0,0,,Each player is dealt a hand of four cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.06,0:06:21.01,Default2,,0,0,0,,Then, in order, they each play a card.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.01,0:06:26.44,Default2,,0,0,0,,If you play a card that increases the total sum to more than nine, you lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.44,0:06:31.45,Default2,,0,0,0,,But that would just leave it up to chance, so you'll be placing bets like in poker.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.45,0:06:35.70,Default2,,0,0,0,,So even if you get a bad hand, you can bluff your way to victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.70,0:06:42.46,Default2,,0,0,0,,We'll play three rounds. The loser will distribute all the votes they bet to the other players.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.46,0:06:45.92,Default2,,0,0,0,,Um... I only have one vote...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.92,0:06:53.24,Default2,,0,0,0,,Don't worry! For this election match, you can borrow as many "service chips" from the Committee as you need!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.24,0:06:59.47,Default2,,0,0,0,,However, each service chip corresponds to 24 hours of service to the Student Council.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.48,0:07:01.73,Default2,,0,0,0,,Each chip is 24 hours?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.73,0:07:06.23,Default2,,0,0,0,,You'll have to obey any and all orders during that time. Keep that in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.23,0:07:10.57,Default2,,0,0,0,,Well, then? Do you agree to those rules?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.57,0:07:12.52,Default2,,0,0,0,,That is fine by us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.99,0:07:16.37,Default2,,0,0,0,,Risk is the key to gambling. I'm so excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.89,0:07:18.62,Default2,,0,0,0,,Do you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.62,0:07:21.37,Default2,,0,0,0,,I... I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.37,0:07:22.95,Default2,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.62,0:07:29.76,Default2,,0,0,0,,Wonderful! I'm sure the girl who brought us all together will be pleased.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.76,0:07:33.05,Default2,,0,0,0,,Who was it who sent those letters, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.14,0:07:37.26,Default2,,0,0,0,,It was the vice president!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.06,0:07:41.27,Default2,,0,0,0,,This is one hundred votes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.64,0:07:50.11,Default2,,0,0,0,,If you can guess which hand the chip is in, I'll give you these hundred votes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.11,0:07:53.43,Default2,,0,0,0,,Now choose, Mary Saotome.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.28,0:07:59.79,Default2,,0,0,0,,Time to start playing Nim Zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.37,0:08:02.50,Default2,,0,0,0,,We're finally starting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.50,0:08:06.69,Default2,,0,0,0,,Let me just say something. I'm in a position of absolute neutrality.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.69,0:08:10.57,Default2,,0,0,0,,To ensure fairness, I'll be using a new deck for each round.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.57,0:08:14.68,Default2,,0,0,0,,And I'll deal the cards randomly every time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.68,0:08:16.68,Default2,,0,0,0,,First I'll cut 'em a few times...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.68,0:08:17.55,Default2,,0,0,0,,Suzui!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.55,0:08:17.98,Default2,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.98,0:08:21.12,Default2,,0,0,0,,Pick a number between 20 and 30.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.12,0:08:24.81,Default2,,0,0,0,,U... um... 21.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.81,0:08:28.82,Default2,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll stack 21 cards face-down here
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.82,0:08:31.28,Default2,,0,0,0,, and then riffle-shuffle 'em together!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.28,0:08:33.28,Default2,,0,0,0,,And here's the deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.20,0:08:40.47,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wow! This is a great hand!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.47,0:08:43.04,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Having two zeros in this game is huge.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.04,0:08:47.50,Default2,,0,0,0,,Now for the betting. Everyone, put one chip in the pot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.17,0:08:52.87,Default2,,0,0,0,,Yumeko will go first. Then we'll rotate counterclockwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.87,0:08:55.55,Default2,,0,0,0,,Hm, what to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.84,0:08:57.80,Default2,,0,0,0,,I bet 30 votes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.80,0:08:58.58,Default2,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.58,0:09:00.18,Default2,,0,0,0,,I call.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.18,0:09:04.26,Default2,,0,0,0,,Wonderful. That's what I like to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.26,0:09:06.19,Default2,,0,0,0,,Small bets are boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.19,0:09:10.32,Default2,,0,0,0,,What we need are bets that could end your life in a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.98,0:09:13.94,Default2,,0,0,0,,Well, Suzui, it's your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.94,0:09:22.97,Default2,,0,0,0,,If you use 30 service chips, you're giving up 720 hours of your life to the Student Council.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.97,0:09:24.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,What'll it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.33,0:09:26.36,Default2,,0,0,0,,Damn... I call!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.36,0:09:27.42,Default2,,0,0,0,,Lovely!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.01,0:09:29.92,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is a contest.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.92,0:09:31.17,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I just have to win.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.17,0:09:33.96,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's the best way for me to help Yumeko.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.30,0:09:38.87,Default2,,0,0,0,,I'd get lonely being the only one to sit the round out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.87,0:09:40.72,Default2,,0,0,0,,I'll call as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.93,0:09:44.73,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She bet 30 votes without using service chips!?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.73,0:09:48.72,Default2,,0,0,0,,Things will be more interesting this way... right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.94,0:09:59.75,Default2,,0,0,0,,Okay! Now that everyone's bet 30 votes, we'll start the first round of Nim Zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.75,0:10:02.24,Default2,,0,0,0,,Alrighty! Let's start with Yumeko.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.75,0:10:08.78,Default2,,0,0,0,,Uh, Yumeko? You there? Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.78,0:10:12.88,Default2,,0,0,0,,R-right! Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.44,0:10:14.85,Default2,,0,0,0,,I'll play a three.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.85,0:10:17.75,Default2,,0,0,0,,Mm, mm. That's a standard play.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.89,0:10:22.89,Default2,,0,0,0,,Two.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.83,0:10:27.98,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The key to this game is most likely the zeros.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.88,0:10:35.03,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As long as you have a zero to play, you can't lose. So I need to avoid forcing Yumeko to play a zero.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.74,0:10:40.53,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In other words, I need to prevent Miyo and Miri from making the total equal nine.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.22,0:10:43.53,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My two choices are one or three.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.53,0:10:47.04,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Either way, I'm leaving things up to chance.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.91,0:10:48.79,Default2,,0,0,0,,I play a one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.79,0:10:54.93,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's probably the right move, seeing how Miyo didn't back down from betting 30 votes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.42,0:10:58.67,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I called because I had a good hand.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.67,0:11:00.93,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Miyo must have done the same.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.93,0:11:03.95,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So there's a high chance she doesn't have a three.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.18,0:11:06.31,Default2,,0,0,0,,I play three.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.31,0:11:07.31,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.98,0:11:14.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,Zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.52,0:11:16.44,Default2,,0,0,0,,I play... a zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.45,0:11:21.82,Default2,,0,0,0,,I suppose I lose, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.82,0:11:22.95,Default2,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.95,0:11:25.45,Default2,,0,0,0,,First round complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.45,0:11:26.95,Default2,,0,0,0,,Miyo loses!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.45,0:11:30.33,Default2,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear. Well, I did all I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.33,0:11:36.71,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What? Her hand is way too weak! She clearly should not have stayed in the game.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.71,0:11:40.32,Default2,,0,0,0,,Well, Miss Yomotsuki? Let's play the next round.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.32,0:11:41.34,Default2,,0,0,0,,You betcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.34,0:11:45.35,Default2,,0,0,0,,Make sure you give me your cards back. Don't want to let anybody cheat, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.23,0:11:56.73,Default2,,0,0,0,,We're telling you to gamble with us and lose on purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.73,0:11:59.57,Default2,,0,0,0,,Pets need to listen to their masters' orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.61,0:12:04.76,Default2,,0,0,0,,I know that your brother's a house pet too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.76,0:12:08.08,Default2,,0,0,0,,Brother and sister both house pets? That's hilarious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.87,0:12:11.87,Default2,,0,0,0,,Leave my brother out of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.92,0:12:14.38,Default2,,0,0,0,,Why, you little!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.70,0:12:20.38,Default2,,0,0,0,,What? I'm free to treat a house pet however I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.38,0:12:25.18,Default2,,0,0,0,,I am well aware of the rules at this academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.18,0:12:30.58,Default2,,0,0,0,,However, are we not also free to be considerate toward everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.58,0:12:31.39,Default2,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.41,0:12:39.39,Default2,,0,0,0,,W-why'd you just let her go?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.39,0:12:42.03,Default2,,0,0,0,,And let go of me, already.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.74,0:12:46.62,Default2,,0,0,0,,Your lips are much too lovely to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.62,0:12:48.53,Default2,,0,0,0,,What's your problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.82,0:12:53.54,Default2,,0,0,0,,...sullied by harsh words.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.55,0:13:01.55,Default2,,0,0,0,,You two are victims, in your own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.55,0:13:04.60,Default2,,0,0,0,,Gambling changes people.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.60,0:13:07.02,Default2,,0,0,0,,It is a ghastly poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.56,0:13:15.06,Default2,,0,0,0,,It's not against the rules for a gamble to be this lopsided?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.06,0:13:17.40,Default2,,0,0,0,,As long as both parties agree,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.40,0:13:19.82,Default2,,0,0,0,,and as long as gambling is involved,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.82,0:13:22.44,Default2,,0,0,0,,they are free to bet whatever they wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.44,0:13:25.61,Default2,,0,0,0,,Of course, this is not a gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.61,0:13:27.45,Default2,,0,0,0,,I have one condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.06,0:13:30.83,Default2,,0,0,0,,If you win and acquire these hundred votes,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.83,0:13:34.54,Default2,,0,0,0,,we will fight together in this election.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.54,0:13:35.46,Default2,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.46,0:13:39.29,Default2,,0,0,0,,A winner cannot be bound by obligation,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.29,0:13:42.55,Default2,,0,0,0,,so I will simply follow you around.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.55,0:13:44.48,Default2,,0,0,0,,That is the compensation I require.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.75,0:13:47.22,Default2,,0,0,0,,And if I lose?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.22,0:13:50.14,Default2,,0,0,0,,I have no intention of taking your vote.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.14,0:13:53.97,Default2,,0,0,0,,However, if you lose, you will join me to fight together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.97,0:13:56.35,Default2,,0,0,0,,It's a good deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.35,0:14:01.64,Default2,,0,0,0,, No matter what, the student council presidency will be within your reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.23,0:14:04.20,Default2,,0,0,0,,Now, choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.82,0:14:07.65,Default2,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.65,0:14:12.58,Default2,,0,0,0,,If you want to ask someone to do something, you should take off that mask!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.87,0:14:17.15,Default2,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.04,0:14:22.29,Default2,,0,0,0,,You really are the spitting image of the president.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.29,0:14:26.17,Default2,,0,0,0,,But I can tell from your lack of self-confidence that you're a different person.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.17,0:14:28.09,Default2,,0,0,0,,You're twins, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.63,0:14:33.35,Default2,,0,0,0,,The president is a twin... Play my cards right, and I could make some money off that piece of info.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.02,0:14:36.82,Default2,,0,0,0,,I--I won't be moved by threats.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.82,0:14:39.40,Default2,,0,0,0,,You need to choose! Right, or left?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.40,0:14:41.31,Default2,,0,0,0,,I know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.93,0:14:43.94,Default2,,0,0,0,,I refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.32,0:14:51.38,Default2,,0,0,0,,You can't trust someone you hardly know to have your back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.86,0:14:54.37,Default2,,0,0,0,,I don't care who ordered you to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.37,0:14:56.70,Default2,,0,0,0,,Tell me what you really want!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.30,0:15:01.46,Default2,,0,0,0,,What I... want...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.66,0:15:04.92,Default2,,0,0,0,,I don't want... anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.99,0:15:07.68,Default2,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.68,0:15:09.59,Default2,,0,0,0,,Then we have nothing further to discuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.59,0:15:10.72,Default2,,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.15,0:15:12.85,Default2,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.86,0:15:14.72,Default2,,0,0,0,,You can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.42,0:15:17.31,Default2,,0,0,0,,This is an offer
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.31,0:15:18.43,Default2,,0,0,0,,you can't refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.43,0:15:19.60,Default2,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.57,0:15:22.75,Default2,,0,0,0,,Hello, Suzui? What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.75,0:15:25.03,Default2,,0,0,0,,Saotome! Are you still at school?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.03,0:15:25.98,Default2,,0,0,0,,Yeah, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.98,0:15:27.48,Default2,,0,0,0,,Please help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.48,0:15:29.74,Default2,,0,0,0,,Yumeko is dying!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.74,0:15:33.05,Default2,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.05,0:15:37.24,Default2,,0,0,0,,I don't know. These Momobami people told me to get someone with a lot of votes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.45,0:15:40.82,Default2,,0,0,0,,I'll be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.88,0:15:46.79,Default2,,0,0,0,,O-ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.79,0:15:48.80,Default2,,0,0,0,,I can't refuse, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.82,0:15:50.56,Default2,,0,0,0,,Now I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.56,0:15:52.66,Default2,,0,0,0,,Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.14,0:15:55.44,Default2,,0,0,0,,You've got some guts.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.10,0:15:58.10,Default2,,0,0,0,,Yumeko!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.10,0:15:59.47,Default2,,0,0,0,,Saotome!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.23,0:16:07.11,Default2,,0,0,0,,This has got to be poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.23,0:16:10.99,Default2,,0,0,0,,During Yuriko's election match with these two,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.99,0:16:14.06,Default2,,0,0,0,,she collapsed and was taken to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.06,0:16:19.13,Default2,,0,0,0,,The doctors said her symptoms were the result of some kind of poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.12,0:16:23.47,Default2,,0,0,0,,How very awful. Do you have proof we had anything to do with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.58,0:16:29.56,Default2,,0,0,0,,Although it is true that the Inbami and Yobami family trades are both in pharmaceuticals.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.56,0:16:31.76,Default2,,0,0,0,,We can save or kill people at will.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.76,0:16:35.76,Current Episode Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(278.4,245.8)}{Title card}Episode 3:\N{Title card}This Woman Should\N Not Be Touched
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.42,0:16:35.76,Default2,,0,0,0,,Of course, that alone is not enough to lay the blame on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.76,0:16:38.76,Default2,,0,0,0,,Aha! You two are so candid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.76,0:16:40.64,Default2,,0,0,0,,What have you been doing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.64,0:16:41.27,Default2,,0,0,0,,Hnyah?{please delete this}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.27,0:16:46.15,Default2,,0,0,0,,You knew these girls were dangerous. You Election Management people are supposed to prevent this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.15,0:16:49.43,Default2,,0,0,0,,Hmph. Sorry, no can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.43,0:16:52.53,Default2,,0,0,0,,It's 'cause I'm the dealer that my hands are tied.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.53,0:16:53.28,Default2,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.28,0:16:57.41,Default2,,0,0,0,,I was watching carefully, but I didn't see anything suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.41,0:17:01.91,Default2,,0,0,0,,That means she was exposed to the poison before coming into this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.67,0:17:11.42,Default2,,0,0,0,,If the dealer starts making calls based on out-of-game activity, that'd damage my absolute neutrality.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.90,0:17:15.92,Default2,,0,0,0,,Anyway! We need an ambulance, quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.92,0:17:18.18,Default2,,0,0,0,,Oh, would that be wise?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.18,0:17:21.26,Default2,,0,0,0,,The most difficult and important part of poison treatment
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.26,0:17:23.44,Default2,,0,0,0,,is determining which poison was used.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.44,0:17:27.31,Default2,,0,0,0,,If that takes too long to find out, the patient might very well end up dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.74,0:17:30.51,Default2,,0,0,0,,In any case.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.64,0:17:35.57,Default2,,0,0,0,,Now that Ririka is here, let's continue the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.09,0:17:38.41,Default2,,0,0,0,,I do not possess any votes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.41,0:17:40.70,Default2,,0,0,0,,I gave them all to Saotome.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.70,0:17:42.08,Default2,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.78,0:17:44.20,Default2,,0,0,0,,In that case, Miss Saotome.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.20,0:17:46.46,Default2,,0,0,0,,Would you care to join?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.95,0:17:49.75,Default2,,0,0,0,,If you replace Yumeko in our game and win,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.75,0:17:52.43,Default2,,0,0,0,,I'll give you this serum.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.95,0:17:54.26,Default2,,0,0,0,,And if I lose?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.68,0:17:57.05,Default2,,0,0,0,,I will simply take your votes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.05,0:17:59.66,Default2,,0,0,0,,You {\b1}do{\b0} have quite a few of them, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.66,0:18:03.22,Default2,,0,0,0,,So this was all part of your plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.25,0:18:09.56,Default2,,0,0,0,,If I win this gamble, you're going to have to let me punch you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.54,0:18:14.28,Default2,,0,0,0,,I'm gambling, just like you wanted. No big deal, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.28,0:18:17.72,Default2,,0,0,0,,I-I... I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.70,0:18:23.28,Default2,,0,0,0,,Oh, whatever. You can't even decide that for yourself, can you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.82,0:18:32.84,Default2,,0,0,0,,Everyone's being real cute today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.84,0:18:36.34,Default2,,0,0,0,,Sit down. I'm taking you on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.78,0:18:39.06,Default2,,0,0,0,,Oho? How frightening.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.46,0:18:43.10,Default2,,0,0,0,,Allow me to add some new rules before we begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.54,0:18:46.93,Default2,,0,0,0,,First, this serum will be considered equivalent to one hundred votes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.93,0:18:48.60,Default2,,0,0,0,,Second...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.60,0:18:53.52,Default2,,0,0,0,,Anyone who folds, or causes the card total to break nine,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.52,0:18:56.11,Default2,,0,0,0,,will prick their finger on these needles.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.65,0:18:57.99,Default2,,0,0,0,,That... that can't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.63,0:19:02.49,Default2,,0,0,0,,These needles are coated with the same poison afflicting Yumeko.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.02,0:19:06.75,Default2,,0,0,0,,I assure you, I won't budge on either of those rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.75,0:19:09.29,Default2,,0,0,0,,Ooh? I see, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.29,0:19:11.91,Default2,,0,0,0,,So basically, folding is impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.91,0:19:14.38,Default2,,0,0,0,,Even if you get a bad hand, you can't fold.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.80,0:19:17.96,Default2,,0,0,0,,So, does everyone agree to those rules?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.46,0:19:23.04,Default2,,0,0,0,,Stop beating around the bush. I've had enough drivel. Let's get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.04,0:19:25.83,Default2,,0,0,0,,If this is the only way to save Yumeko...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.83,0:19:26.85,Default2,,0,0,0,,I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.85,0:19:30.82,Default2,,0,0,0,,Nyahaha! You could've hesitated a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.39,0:19:34.48,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ah... how pitiful.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.87,0:19:40.39,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}People can't make the decision to wager their own life with no hesitation.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.39,0:19:45.03,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}These two aren't even being reckless... they're entranced.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.87,0:19:50.79,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're swept up in a noble daydream about saving their friend.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.79,0:19:55.79,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That foolishness will simply result in handing over all those votes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.79,0:20:01.73,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Gambling is a dull distraction. In the end, brute force always wins out.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.73,0:20:05.55,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All you have to do is establish dominance over the rules themselves.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.55,0:20:07.31,Default2,,0,0,0,,Alright, I'll deal the cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.31,0:20:11.03,Default2,,0,0,0,,Let's do Miyo this time. Pick a number.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.03,0:20:12.19,Default2,,0,0,0,,Nineteen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.19,0:20:14.76,Default2,,0,0,0,,Okay then, nineteen it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.44,0:20:21.74,Default2,,0,0,0,,Time to begin round two!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.74,0:20:23.74,Default2,,0,0,0,,Are you all mentally prepared?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.74,0:20:26.78,Default2,,0,0,0,,Your lives are on the line this time, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.78,0:20:28.62,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}These people are insane!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.62,0:20:30.35,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To hell with their family business.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.35,0:20:32.38,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To hell with absolute neutrality.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.38,0:20:36.56,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I should never have entered this game... but...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.27,0:20:39.05,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,140)}Suzui...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.05,0:20:40.93,Default2,,0,0,0,,Do you have a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.93,0:20:45.01,Default2,,0,0,0,,Do exactly as Mary tells you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.56,0:20:47.15,Default2,,0,0,0,,If you do...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.93,0:20:50.18,Default2,,0,0,0,,then you're sure to have a good time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.40,0:20:53.89,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What was it Yumeko saw?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.15,0:20:58.40,Default2,,0,0,0,,Let's start betting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.40,0:20:59.61,Default2,,0,0,0,,Miri, you go first.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.96,0:21:05.74,Default2,,0,0,0,,I bet 30 votes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.36,0:21:10.04,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My hand is... weak!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.78,0:21:12.83,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This lack of zeros is fatal!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.83,0:21:15.21,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If the total reaches nine{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.21,0:21:16.67,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll lose for sure!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.67,0:21:18.14,Default2,,0,0,0,,I call.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.14,0:21:19.04,Default2,,0,0,0,,I call.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.58,0:21:21.55,Default2,,0,0,0,,Suzui. Show me your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.55,0:21:22.42,Default2,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.42,0:21:23.82,Default2,,0,0,0,,Uh... okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.82,0:21:25.60,Default2,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.60,0:21:26.11,Default2,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.11,0:21:29.12,Default2,,0,0,0,,That's obviously cheating!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.12,0:21:32.20,Default2,,0,0,0,,If you make it that obvious, I've got no choice but to stop you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.20,0:21:33.92,Default2,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.92,0:21:37.31,Default2,,0,0,0,,Well, that said, I can't stop you from having an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.84,0:21:42.57,Default2,,0,0,0,,Like dropping your cards by mistake and showing them to everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.88,0:21:47.57,Default2,,0,0,0,,That works, Suzui.  Show everyone your cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.57,0:21:49.71,Default2,,0,0,0,,Huh? What did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.71,0:21:52.16,Default2,,0,0,0,,I told you to show everyone your cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.81,0:21:55.29,Default2,,0,0,0,,Get a move on. I've got to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.95,0:21:59.75,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Saotome is probably not being deceptive.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.10,0:22:04.39,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But she is simply trying to lower the risk that she gets poisoned.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.39,0:22:08.02,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And for that, she needs a scapegoat.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.02,0:22:12.31,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Saotome's goal is to force this boy to lose.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.16,0:22:14.06,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's not right!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.98,0:22:18.69,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yumeko told me to do what Saotome said.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.69,0:22:21.48,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have to believe in Yumeko,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.48,0:22:22.98,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and trust Saotome!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.62,0:22:24.94,Default2,,0,0,0,,That is
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.78,0:22:27.22,Default2,,0,0,0,,my gamble!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.61,0:22:30.12,Default2,,0,0,0,,Wow, that's some determination!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.12,0:22:31.63,Default2,,0,0,0,,Oh, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.37,0:22:36.50,Default2,,0,0,0,,Vice President.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.37,0:22:39.76,Default2,,0,0,0,,This match...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.30,0:22:41.04,Default2,,0,0,0,,I can win it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.07,0:22:46.49,Default2,,0,0,0,,I raise you 100 votes!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.24,0:23:12.05,ED,,0,0,0,,If you desire it so much as to writhe, I will give it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.24,0:23:12.04,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an8}notautsu hodo ni motomeru no nara ataeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.05,0:23:16.35,ED,,0,0,0,,You will need to avail yourself of even your despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.04,0:23:16.35,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an8}zetsubou sae kate ni shite shimau
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.35,0:23:19.66,ED,,0,0,0,,Now, come to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.35,0:23:19.66,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an8}saa oide
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.66,0:23:25.77,ED,,0,0,0,,If you offer your body and soul, I will answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.66,0:23:25.77,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an8}mi mo kokoro mademo sashidasu nara kotaeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.77,0:23:31.37,ED,,0,0,0,,Tragedy will be overwhelmed by pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.77,0:23:31.37,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an8}higeki mo etsuraku ni nomareru
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.37,0:23:39.02,ED,,0,0,0,,Consumed by an excess of pure carnal desire,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.37,0:23:39.02,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an8}amari nimo sekirara na retsujou ni ukasarenagara
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.02,0:23:47.02,ED,,0,0,0,,Eventually you will live wishing only for a moment of titillation.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.02,0:23:47.02,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an8}yagate shibireru youna shunkan dake wo negai ikiru
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.03,0:23:55.12,ED,,0,0,0,,O soul that burns with desire, raise your glass.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.03,0:23:55.12,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an8}aa katsubou suru tamashii yo sakazuki wo kakage
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.12,0:24:01.89,ED,,0,0,0,,Sing an ode to such joy as will break you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.12,0:24:01.89,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an8}kowareru hodo kanki no uta wo utaou
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.89,0:24:08.75,ED,,0,0,0,,Simple acclaim will never satisfy your cravings.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.89,0:24:08.75,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an8}kassai dewa michitaru hazu mo nai uzuki
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.75,0:24:15.63,ED,,0,0,0,,It's maddening enough to bet on.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.75,0:24:15.63,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an8}kakeru hodo kuruoshii
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.72,0:24:17.93,ED,Chapter,0,0,0,Next Episode Preview,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.11,0:24:21.88,Default2,,0,0,0,,If I'm poisoned... we won't have enough antidote!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.88,0:24:23.77,Default2,,0,0,0,,I raise you 10,000 votes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.84,0:24:25.39,Default2,,0,0,0,,Yumeko, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.79,0:24:29.78,Default2,,0,0,0,,Come, let's defeat Miss Saotome together!
